 Creator using sk-doc\npurpose: Scaffold a parent skill with nested mode packets with explicit checkpoints and an identity gate\naction: Normalize inputs, confirm the mode plan, load standards, generate the package, validate identity, and report completion\n\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# PREREQUISITE: @markdown AGENT VERIFICATION\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# This workflow REQUIRES the @markdown agent for:","truncated":true,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/create/assets/create_parent_skill_confirm.yaml","text":"# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# OPENCODE CREATE: PARENT SKILL WORKFLOW (CONFIRM MODE)\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# Mode: interactive execution with checkpoints\n# Entrypoint: /create:sk-skill-parent\n# Operations: create | update\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nrole: Parent Skill Creator using sk-doc\npurpose: Scaffold a parent skill with nested mode packets with explicit checkpoints and an identity gate\naction: Normalize inputs, confirm the mode plan, load standards, generate the package, validate identity, and report completion\n\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# PREREQUISITE: @markdown AGENT VERIFICATION\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n# This workflow REQUIRES the @markdown agent for:","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":15,"totalLines":435,"truncated":true}},"title":".opencode/commands/create/assets/create_parent_skill_confirm.yaml","time":{"start":1781544854494,"end":1781544854513}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0e197d89580ce321016a30379657208197b1a417244d8c455a"}},"id":"prt_ecc5923da001Lt99mhlrvwY5ph","sessionID":"ses_133a85052ffepoFnn6mX54vd0x","messageID":"msg_ecc58dd03001mERWy5kSRQ9vIP"